g of \'\'{{wp|scorpion}}\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Poison|type2=Bug\n|ja=スコルピ \'\'Scorupi\'\'|jameaning=From a shortening of \'\'scorpion\'\'.\n|de=Pionskora|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Skorpion|scorpion}}\'\'.\n|fr=Rapion|frmeaning=From \'\'scorpion\'\'.\n|es=Skorupi|esmeaning=Same as English name.\n|it=Skorupi|itmeaning=Same as English name.\n|ko=스콜피 \'\'Skorupi\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of Japanese name.\n|zh_cmn=紫天蠍 \'\'Zǐ Tiān Xiē\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=Literally "Purple sky scorpion". 天蠍 also refers to the constellation {{wp|Scorpius}}.\n|hi=स्करुपाइ \'\'Skorupi\'\'|himeaning=Transliteration of English name}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Poison|type2=Bug}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Poison|prevnum=450|prev=Hippowdon|nextnum=452|next=Drapion}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Pionskora]]\n[[es:Skorupi]]\n[[fr:Rapion]]\n[[it:Skorupi]]\n[[ja:スコルピ]]\n[[zh:钳尾蝎]]'}